Title: Lift Mein Phasi Vandana - Wagle Ki Duniya - Ep 533 - Full Episode - 15 Dec 2022
Description: Episode 533: Lift Mein Phasi Vandana ---------------------------------------- With Vandana unconscious and confined in the elevator  Rajesh and the Wagle family are in a panic.
